snippet.title: Dragon Ball Z: Extreme Butoden - 3DS - Ready! Fight! (English Launch Trailer)
snippet.description:
Dragon Ball Z: Extreme Butoden is available this Friday, Oct. 16th! Join the fight with 25 playable characters and over 100 characters from the Dragon Ball Universe! 

It isn't too late to pre-order the game and get Super Butoden 2 for free, early access to 6 Z-Assist Characters (Retail offer only) and a Nintendo 3DS Home Screen Theme (Digital offer only)!

Want to win the game and awesome goodies? Share your energy and fight on http://bnent.eu/DBZXBbattle ! 
 
Official Facebook page: www.facebook.com/DBZ.videogames
